Revision history for Plack-Middleware-Text-Minify:

v0.2.1    2021-09-19 11:26:10+01:00 Europe/London
  [Bug Fixes]
  - Upgrade minimum version of Text::Minify::XS to v0.4.8 to improve
    handling of malformed UTF-8.

v0.2.0    2021-05-21 14:05:48+01:00 Europe/London
  [Enhancements]
  - Do not minify if the `psgix.no-minify` key is true.

v0.1.6    2021-05-15 17:10:03+01:00 Europe/London
  [Documentation]
  - Added note about multiple newlines.

v0.1.5    2021-05-06 12:57:13+01:00 Europe/London
  [Bug Fixes]
  - Bump minimum version of Text::Minify::XS to v0.4.0.

  [Documentation]
  - Added note about whitespace cleanup in templating systems.

  [Tests]
  - Add more author tests.

v0.1.4    2021-01-05 14:29:37+00:00 Europe/London
  [Bug Fixes]
  - Upgrade minimum version of Text::Minify::XS to v0.3.6, GH#2.

  [Tests]
  - Add tests for handling of empty results.

v0.1.3    2021-01-04 14:03:38+00:00 Europe/London
  [Bug Fixes]
  - Upgrade minimum version of Text::Minify::XS to v0.3.3.

  [Documentation]
  - Bump copyright year.

v0.1.2    2021-01-04 13:32:20+00:00 Europe/London
  [Bug Fixes]
  - Fix how Content-Length header is updated.

v0.1.1    2020-12-28 17:29:28+00:00 Europe/London
  [Enhancements]
  - Downgrade minimum version to v5.9.3 (same as Text::Minify::XS).

  [Bug Fixes]
  - Skip if the response is missing a body.

  - Skip if the response code does not have a body, GH#1.

  - Skip if the request is not a GET or POST request, GH#1.

  - Update the Content-Length header, if it is set.

  [Documentation]
  - Add note to KNOWN ISSUES about older Perl versions.

v0.1.0    2020-12-11 12:15:09+00:00 Europe/London
  - Initial release.
